{"tid":1943534,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"世界很亂","createTime":"2020-03-25T18:20:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T00:28:19.000Z","uid":209522,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"60560400cbe7f950428cbc38bd71ba64860e5e61","tid":1943534,"uid":209522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T18:20:12.000Z","msg":"人生很苦 但你要甜<br />\n已經盡量樂觀啲<br />\n成日都覺得下年會更好<br />\n點知一年衰過一年 做咩都好似有阻滯咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時會無啦啦有傷心既感覺<br />\n間唔中又會發惡夢<br />\n諗住做下gym個人會開心啲 點知依家連gym都無得做<br />\n係咁飲酒又會好撚肥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有時覺得人生充滿唔同挑戰 要學會勇敢<br />\n有時又覺得世界太多誘惑 所有野都變得好奢侈<br />\n真係令人又愛又恨<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894c044aabe3acfd50817b132e2fe8680a59f284","tid":1943534,"uid":431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T19:46:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0029267d3bc8f2550c2244eb5064723700d55f2","tid":1943534,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-25T20:06:37.000Z","msg":"世界很美 因為有我肥boy<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4666aa80a2023ee8de8ea1f9af9a0c7556c150ae","tid":1943534,"uid":209522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T00:18:34.000Z","msg":"又失眠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌"},{"pid":"5c6ab97f86c45918033beda10165bdcef018ee6e","tid":1943534,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T00:28:19.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">惡運到盡頭<br />\n好景即將降臨<br />\n明天將更近</span></strong>"}]}